flowchart TD

%% ========================
%% SOURCE MANAGEMENT
%% ========================
A[Maintainer adds new API source] --> B[Update sources.json]
B --> C[Workflow 1: Weekly Source Discovery]

C --> D{New source detected?}
D -- No --> E[Do nothing]
D -- Yes --> F[Assign source to batch]
F --> G[Update batch registry]

%% ========================
%% DAILY SYNC WORKFLOW
%% ========================
G --> H[Workflow 2: Daily Sync + Versioning]
H --> I[Select next batch]

I --> J[Iterate sources in batch]

J --> K[Send conditional request (ETag / Last-Modified)]

K --> L{Changed?}

L -- No --> M[Skip source]
L -- Yes --> N[Fetch full OpenAPI spec]

%% ========================
%% CHANGE DETECTION
%% ========================
N --> O[Normalize spec]
O --> P[Generate hash]
P --> Q{Hash changed?}

Q -- No --> M
Q -- Yes --> R[Trigger pipeline]

%% ========================
%% PIPELINE PROCESSING
%% ========================
R --> S[Parse OpenAPI]
S --> T[Extract endpoints]
T --> U[Normalize data]
U --> V[Enrich metadata (tags, category)]
V --> W[Generate templates (API Dash format)]

%% ========================
%% VALIDATION
%% ========================
W --> X[Validation Layer]
X --> Y{Valid?}

Y -- No --> Z[Reject update, keep old version]
Y -- Yes --> AA[Create new version folder]

%% ========================
%% STORAGE
%% ========================
AA --> AB[Store templates in repo]
AB --> AC[Update per-API index]
AC --> AD[Update global index]

AD --> AE[Commit to GitHub repo]

%% ========================
%% DISTRIBUTION
%% ========================
AE --> AF[jsDelivr CDN caches files]

%% ========================
%% CLIENT SIDE
%% ========================
AF --> AG[Client App Launch]
AG --> AH[Fetch global index.json]

AH --> AI[Render categories + API list]

AI --> AJ[User searches / browses]

AJ --> AK[User selects API]
AK --> AL[Fetch per-API index]

AL --> AM[Render endpoint list]

AM --> AN[User selects endpoint]
AN --> AO[Fetch template file]

AO --> AP[Load into API Dash editor]

AP --> AQ[User edits request]
AQ --> AR[User executes request]

AR --> AS[External API responds]
AS --> AT[Display response to user]

%% ========================
%% VERSION SWITCH FLOW
%% ========================
AM --> AU[User selects different version]
AU --> AV[Fetch version-specific per-API index]
AV --> AM